text: SNAFU is the second studio album by Potty Mouth. It was released on March 1, 2019, six years after their first album Hell Bent. ==Track listing== ==Personnel== ;Potty Mouth * Abby Weems - lead vocals, background vocals, guitar * Victoria Mandanas - drums, background vocals * Ally Einbinder - bass ;Additional personnel * Courtney Ballard - production ==References== Category:2019 albums Category:Pop albums by American artists Category:Pop rock albums by American artists
